OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773677476
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused yet to
OL,4,Csecure fresh legal representation
OL,6,FA Co Antrim man awaiting trial for
OL,7,Fmurdering Chloe Mitchell has been
OL,8,Funable to secure fresh legal
OL,9,Frepresentation, Belfast Crown Court
OL,10,Fhas been told.
OL,12,FBrandon John Rainey's legal team
OL,13,Fwithdrew from representing him last
OL,14,FThursday, citing they had been
OL,15,F"professionally compromised''.
OL,17,FRainey, 29, of James Street,
OL,18,FBallymena, denies murdering the 21-
OL,19,Fyear-old on June 3, 2023, and
OL,20,Fpreventing the lawful burial of her
OL,21,Fremains.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
