OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773677476
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused yet to
OL,4,Csecure fresh legal representation
OL,6,FThe defendant was produced to court
OL,7,Fagain on Monday after Madam Justice
OL,8,FMcBride told him last week to find new
OL,9,Flegal representation and have them
OL,10,Fpresent for the hearing.
OL,12,FStanding in the dock, he was asked by
OL,13,FMadam Justice McBride had he been able
OL,14,Fto secure fresh legal representation.
OL,16,FRainey replied: "I was talking to a
OL,17,Flaw firm prior to my barristers
OL,18,Fdeclining (his case) and he said he
OL,19,Fcan't take the case on.''
OL,26,@zD@KpmzD@Tpn
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773677476
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused yet to
OL,4,Csecure fresh legal representation
OL,6,FHe said since then he has spoken with
OL,7,Fa solicitor in Lurgan, Co Armagh.
OL,9,F"He says he doesn't think he has the
OL,10,Ftime, he would need to have two new
OL,11,Fbarristers in. He said that in his
OL,12,Fapproach to the case he feels he might
OL,13,Fnot be able to touch it.
OL,15,F"He feels that if he came in with two
OL,16,Fnew barristers he would not have the
OL,17,Fright amount of time to build up his
OL,18,Fcase. I think he feels the pressure of
OL,19,Ftime,'' said Rainey.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773677476
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused yet to
OL,4,Csecure fresh legal representation
OL,6,F"I spoke with him on Friday but I had
OL,7,Fno luck with anyone else over the
OL,8,Fweekends as they were all shut.''
OL,10,FHe confirmed to Madam Justice McBride
OL,11,Fthat he still wanted a solicitor and
OL,12,Ftwo barristers to act on his behalf at
OL,13,Fhis trial.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773677476
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused yet to
OL,4,Csecure fresh legal representation
OL,6,FRainey said that under prison rules,
OL,7,Fhe was only allowed a maximum of four
OL,8,For five legal teams on his phone at
OL,9,Fone time and if he had to contact a
OL,10,Ffurther legal team he would have to
OL,11,Fremove all previous solicitors'
OL,12,Ftelephone numbers before adding a new
OL,13,Ffirm.
OL,15,F"Your calls have to be approved due to
OL,16,Fprison procedures. It's a whole
OL,17,Frigmarole,'' added the defendant.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
