PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773677476
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused yet to
OL,4,Csecure fresh legal representation
OL,6,FChloe Mitchell's family were present
OL,7,Fin the public gallery with her sister
OL,8,Fshouting towards Rainey before being
OL,9,Fushered out of the court.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Rainey's father also
OL,12,Fattempted to speak but Madam Justice
OL,13,FMcBride told him: "Sorry, Mr Rainey.
OL,14,FThis is a review of an important case.
OL,16,F"Your son has spoken on his own behalf
OL,17,Fand it is not an opportunity for other
OL,18,Fpeople to speak.''
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773677476
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused yet to
OL,4,Csecure fresh legal representation
OL,6,FThe senior judge said she would review
OL,7,FRainey's case this Friday, March 20,
OL,8,F2026, and she told the defendant that
OL,9,Fbetween now and then he should
OL,10,Fendeavour to secure fresh legal
OL,11,Frepresentation.
OL,13,F"I don't know the administrative
OL,14,Fprocedures within the prison but I
OL,15,Fwould ask that all steps are taken to
OL,16,Fenable you to secure legal
OL,17,Frepresentation as soon as possible,''
OL,18,Fsaid Madam Justice McBride.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773677476
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused yet to
OL,4,Csecure fresh legal representation
OL,6,F"And if the administrative
OL,7,Farrangements can be changed to
OL,8,Faccommodate you then I would ask that
OL,9,Fthat is done.''
OL,11,FThe judge told Rainey that if he does
OL,12,Fsecure a new solicitor then they
OL,13,Fshould attend court for the review
OL,14,Fhearing on Friday, March 20.
OL,16,FAt the request of the prosecution,
OL,17,FMadam Justice McBride said she would
OL,18,Fmaintain the trial date of Monday,
OL,19,FApril 13, 2026, until such time as an
OL,20,Fapplication was made to vacate it.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
