OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773677476
OL,3,CChloe Mitchell murder accused yet to
OL,4,Csecure fresh legal representation
OL,6,FChloe Mitchell's remains were found
OL,7,Fdays after she went missing.
OL,9,FShe was last seen alive on CCTV in
OL,10,FBallymena town centre in the early
OL,11,Fhours of June 3, 2023 and an extensive
OL,12,Fsearch operation was launched by the
OL,13,FPSNI.
OL,15,FDetectives investigating her
OL,16,Fdisappearance later launched a murder
OL,17,Finquiry after human remains were
OL,18,Fdiscovered in the Co Antrim town.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
